      </div>
      <div class="card-section-label" style="margin-top:16px">REPUTATION SCORE</div>
      <div class="rep-bar-wrap">
        <div class="rep-bar"><div class="rep-fill" style="width:94%"></div></div>
        <span class="rep-score">94 / 100</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rep-note">Based on on-chain task history, attestations, and deployer stake</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="fig-caption">Agents build trust in hours, not decades. Identity is provenance, not authentication.</div>
</div>

<style>
  .fig-wrap {
    border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: #111;
    padding: 24px;
    margin: 2.5em 0;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  }
  .fig-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .card-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .card-left, .card-right {
    background: #181818;
    border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 16px;
  }
  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .card-avatar {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #2a3a2a;
    border: 1px solid #5a9a5a;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #5a9a5a;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .card-handle {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #e0e0e0;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .card-did {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #555;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .risk-badge {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .risk-low { background: #1a3a1a; color: #5a9a5a; border: 1px solid #2a5a2a; }
  .risk-med { background: #3a2a1a; color: #f0a500; border: 1px solid #5a4a1a; }
  .card-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .stat {
    background: #111;
    border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 10px;
  }
  .stat-value {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #e0e0e0;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .stat-label { font-size: 9px; color: #555; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .card-section-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #444;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .attestations { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
  .attest { font-size: 11px; }
  .attest-ok { color: #5a9a5a; }
  .attest-warn { color: #f0a500; }
  .log { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .log-entry {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #666;
  }
  .log-time { color: #444; min-width: 36px; }
  .log-ok { color: #5a9a5a; }
  .log-text { color: #888; }
  .rep-bar-wrap {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 8px 0 6px;
  }
  .rep-bar {
    flex: 1;
    height: 4px;
    background: #222;
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .rep-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: #5a9a5a;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .rep-score { font-size: 12px; color: #5a9a5a; white-space: nowrap; }
  .rep-note { font-size: 9px; color: #444; line-height: 1.4; }
  .fig-caption {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #555;
    margin-top: 16px;
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .card-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .card-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>
